arStrings.szText: When you use a {c_important}Subterfuge{/c} Skill, leave behind an unstable {c_important}Shadow Decoy Trap{/c} that Taunts enemies. The {c_important}Shadow Decoy Trap{/c} will explode after {c_number}[Affix_Value_1|1|]{/c} seconds dealing {c_random}[Affix_Flat_Value_1]{/c} Shadow damage. Cannot occur more than once every {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} seconds.
